Create a page showing your daily routine:
•	Use <h1> for title 
•	<h2> for Morning, Afternoon, Evening 
•	Add paragraphs under each 

3. Favorite Websites List
Create:
•	An unordered list of 5 websites 
•	Convert it into clickable links 
•	Make at least 2 links open in a new tab 

4. Image Gallery
Create a simple gallery:
•	Add 3 images 
•	Set different widths for each 
•	Add proper alt text 

5. Student Table
